import io
import random
import requests
from PIL import Image, ImageDraw, ImageFont
from apps import App, ExecutionContext
from frame.image_utils import draw_text_with_border

class CodeApp(App):
    def run(self, context: ExecutionContext):
        context.state['options'] = self.config.get('options', '').strip().split('\n')
        context.state['keyword'] = self.config.get('keyword', '')
        if not context.state['keyword']:
            context.state['keyword'] = random.choice(context.state['options'])

import io
import random
import requests
from PIL import Image, ImageDraw, ImageFont
from apps import App, ExecutionContext
from frame.image_utils import draw_text_with_border

class CodeApp(App):
    def run(self, context: ExecutionContext):
        random.shuffle(context.state['options'])
